            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The most common inputs are IP-based location, device type, referral source, purchase history, CRM segment, cookies, and on-site behavior. Deeper stacks add CDP profiles and predictive-audience scores.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

